          <p>Pictured • Team members would have morning tea and g-nuts (like peanuts, but smaller) with students at Hannah Moshi School • Team members helped students create life maps, writing out events that have shaped them, to share with their sponsors • At church: A translator helps the team share Bible stories using a storying cloth.</p>

